					"value": "Playing as a paladin break your oath and start a long rest.\r\nFastest way would be:\r\n1. Start as a paladin.\r\n2. recon infiniteAp\r\n3. spawnCharacter Drow_Male_Civilian_Lolth_05447998-ac54-4394-8d56-39739d7ed948\r\n4. Go into FTB, kill the civilian.\r\nor\r\n1. Start with a paladin.\r\n2. oe MakeOathbreaker"
